-----------------------------------------------
glSVG
-----------------------------------------------

A python library for displaying SVG files
using opengl.

-----------------------------------------------
Usage
-----------------------------------------------

    import glsvg

    # initialize opengl context
    # ...

    # load svg file
    svgObj = glsvg.SVG(filename)

    # draw svg file
    svgObj.draw(x,y)


